			<h3 class='section_title'>WANT TO ATTEND?</h3>
			<a class='signup' id='attendee_signup' href='https://www.eventbrite.com/e/socal-virtual-reality-conference-tickets-17008690451' target='_blank'>PURCHASE TICKETS</a>
		</div>
